  abstract  = {Tikhonov--Phillips regularization is one of the best-known regularization methods for inverse problems. A posteriori criteria for determining the regularization parameter $\alpha$ require solving $$(*) (A^*A+\alpha I) x =A^* y^{\delta}$$ for different values of $\alpha$.\par
