  comment   = {{\bf Introduction} {\em 'Since the information which the pulse affords is of so great importance, and so often consulted, surely it must be to our advantage to appreciate fully all it tells us, and to draw from it every detail that it is capable of imparting'} F.A. Mahomed 1872 [1]\par
